title: /serverless/DAYS Sydney
eventShortDescription:
/serverless/DAYS will be an in-person event, held on 21st May at Wesley Conference Center in Sydney. It's a 1-day community-run event comprised of talks and networking among active developers and technical leaders across Australia & New Zealand.

SSW & Tina are proud to sponsor this event. We are hosting the after party, RSVP here.
Meet us there! 🙂

Note: SSW does not host this event.
